caption: My bf used to be a big fan of the spot so we ordered two poke bowls a week ago. Mine went through well since they put what I chose on online. However his bowl was terrible. He ordered salmon and shrimp as protein and there were only 3 tiny peaces of salmon and bunch of tiny shrimp meat. Also some other ingredients were missing like Nori, sesame seeds, and mango.
